4-46:Event threading is strongly related to topic detection and tracking, but also different from it significantly .
4-47:It goes beyond topics, and models the relationships between events .
4-48:Thus, event threading can be considered as a further extension of topic detection and tracking and is more challenging due to at least the following difficulties. .
