9-42:We first train our models on the 26 training topics .
9-43:Training involves learning the best threshold Ì for each of the models .
9-44:We then test the performances of all the trained models on the 27 test topics .
9-45:We evaluate our performance 451 using the average values of Dependency Precision (DP), Dependency Recall and Dependency F measure .
9-46:We consider the complete link model to be our baseline since for each event, it trivially considers all earlier events to be parents .
